TheCurrent, one of the Minnesota Public Radio stations, routinely places links for purchase of songs on its website – this is not banned under any advertising law. Amazon linking to products spoken about is also very much part of how the public radio site proceeds online – and they do all this while honoring specific laws that do not allow them to advertise.
